hey conclude with a model statute that could serve as the basis of a serious congressional effort to restore Americans’ faith in democratic politics.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aCampaign fundsxUnited StatesxUnited States. 0aCampaign fundszUnited States. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / Political Process / Campaigns & Elections.2bisacsh1 aAyres, Ian, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030012701040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300127010423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300127010/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles